## Agent Office — Cursor Rules

- Godot 4.2, GDScript, Forward Plus renderer
- SettingsManager is an autoload singleton — access directly, never instantiate
- All API calls go through OpenClaw gateway (OpenAI-compatible endpoints)
- Scenes use CSGBox3D for geometry (prototyping stage, not final meshes)
- Settings menu is built in code (no .tscn), uses _add_slider helper
- Tests are headless: `godot --headless --script tests/run_tests.gd`
- Each room needs: walls, Area3D trigger, avatar, TTSPlayer, door label, agent_configs entry
- Chat uses BBCode in RichTextLabel (cyan=user, yellow=agent, gray=system, red=error)
- Voice flow: AudioEffectCapture → WAV → STT → chat → TTS → AudioStreamPlayer3D
- Read AGENTS.md for full architecture and file map
